---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../../data/site';
import CTASection from '../../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Comprehensive Eye Exams in Phoenix, AZ" description="A complete evaluation of your vision and eye health. Routine eye exams in Phoenix with prescription updates and screening for glaucoma, cataracts, and macular degeneration." pageType="service">

  <section class="hero-bg">
    <div class="container-x py-20 lg:py-28">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <a href="/services" class="inline-flex items-center text-gold text-xs uppercase tracking-extra-wide font-semibold mb-6 hover:text-gold-dark transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 16l-4-4m0 0l4-4m-4 4h18" /></svg>
            All Services
          </a>
          <span class="eyebrow">Service</span>
          <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl mt-6 mb-8 leading-[1.1]">Comprehensive<br/><span class="text-gold">Eye Exams.</span></h1>
          <span class="gold-rule"></span>
          <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-navy/80 leading-relaxed mb-10">
            A thorough check of your vision and your eye health — using modern diagnostic tools and unhurried, attentive care.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href={`tel:${SITE.phoneRaw}`} class="btn-primary">Schedule Your Exam</a>
            <a href={SITE.intakeFormUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-secondary">New Patient Intake</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 flex justify-center">
          <div class="relative w-64 lg:w-80">
            <div class="absolute -inset-3 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-gold/25 to-sage/15 blur-2xl rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="aspect-square overflow-hidden rounded-full ring-1 ring-navy/10 shadow-2xl">
              <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534627425233-f7d6335ca734?q=80&w=900&auto=format&fit=crop"
                alt="Detailed close-up of a human eye and iris"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                width="700"
                height="700"
                loading="eager"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 lg:py-32 bg-white">
    <div class="container-x">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-6 text-base lg:text-lg text-navy/80 leading-relaxed">
          <div>
            <span class="eyebrow">What's Included</span>
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl mt-6 mb-6">More Than an Updated Prescription.</h2>
            <span class="gold-rule"></span>
          </div>
          <p>A comprehensive eye exam isn't just about how clearly you see today — it's a check on the long-term health of your eyes. Many eye diseases, including glaucoma and diabetic retinopathy, develop slowly and without symptoms. By the time you notice a change in your vision, damage may already be done.</p>
          <p>That's why we recommend an annual exam, even if your vision feels stable. Catching issues early makes them dramatically more treatable.</p>
          <p>Every exam at Paradise Valley Eye Docs includes a vision assessment, an eye-health evaluation, and screening for the conditions most likely to affect your vision over time. We take the time to explain what we find, answer your questions, and recommend next steps that actually fit your life.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <div class="bg-cream p-8 lg:p-10">
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg uppercase tracking-extra-wide mb-6">We Screen For</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-navy/80">
              <li class="border-b border-warmgray-dark/40 pb-4">
                <div class="font-semibold text-navy mb-1">Refractive errors</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-navy/70">Nearsightedness, farsightedness, astigmatism, and presbyopia</div>
              </li>
              <li class="border-b border-warmgray-dark/40 pb-4">
                <div class="font-semibold text-navy mb-1">Glaucoma</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-navy/70">Pressure-related damage to the optic nerve</div>
              </li>
              <li class="border-b border-warmgray-dark/40 pb-4">
                <div class="font-semibold text-navy mb-1">Cataracts</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-navy/70">Clouding of the eye's natural lens</div>
              </li>
              <li class="border-b border-warmgray-dark/40 pb-4">
                <div class="font-semibold text-navy mb-1">Macular degeneration</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-navy/70">Age-related vision loss in the central retina</div>
              </li>
              <li class="border-b border-warmgray-dark/40 pb-4">
                <div class="font-semibold text-navy mb-1">Diabetic eye disease</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-navy/70">Retinal changes linked to diabetes</div>
              </li>
              <li class="pb-0">
                <div class="font-semibold text-navy mb-1">Dry eye disease</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-navy/70">Tear-film instability and inflammation</div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 lg:py-32 bg-cream">
    <div class="container-x">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <span class="eyebrow">When to Schedule</span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl mt-6 mb-6">How Often Should You Come In?</h2>
        <span class="gold-rule mx-auto"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 lg:p-10 border-l-4 border-gold">
          <div class="font-display text-2xl text-gold mb-3">Every Year</div>
          <p class="text-navy/75 leading-relaxed text-sm">For most adults — even if your vision feels fine. Many eye conditions have no early symptoms.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 lg:p-10 border-l-4 border-gold">
          <div class="font-display text-2xl text-gold mb-3">Every Year (Kids)</div>
          <p class="text-navy/75 leading-relaxed text-sm">School-age children should have annual exams — undiagnosed vision issues can affect learning.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 lg:p-10 border-l-4 border-gold">
          <div class="font-display text-2xl text-gold mb-3">Sooner If…</div>
          <p class="text-navy/75 leading-relaxed text-sm">You're noticing blur, eye strain, headaches, sudden flashes or floaters, or have diabetes or a family history of eye disease.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection />
</BaseLayout>
